        <scopecontent id="ref1">
            <head>Scope and Contents note</head>
            <p>Stephen C. Vladeck was the husband of Judith Vladeck and worked as a labor and civil rights lawyer and collective bargainer in higher education. Vladeck was also counsel to and secretary-treasurer of the Peoples Educational Camp Society, an active member of the Tamiment Institute and Robert F. Wagner Labor Archives at New York University. This collection contains some of Vladeck's personal and professional correspondence from the 1950s and 1960s.</p>
